  "3151020": {
    "name": "Easy Ball Game",
    "steam_appid": 3151020,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>If you're looking for a challenge, you've found it!  </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Easy Ball Game is a brand new game that unlike its name is an extremely difficult game based on the Only UP style of play!  </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Climbing has you rolling, jumping and testing your balance. </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>The game consists of several zones with different graphic styles and obstacles all to be discovered. </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3151020/extras/e4c118373fa3cfd8da1767dda4338bdf.poster.avif?t=1758631446\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3151020/extras/e4c118373fa3cfd8da1767dda4338bdf.webm?t=1758631446\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3151020/extras/e4c118373fa3cfd8da1767dda4338bdf.mp4?t=1758631446\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>You can change skins to your ball and unlock new ones! </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>For the first time in the genre there are also NPCs, which interact with you and give you funny tips and comments!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3151020/extras/cb9e75aae2940b02e630208bc930f745.poster.avif?t=1758631446\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3151020/extras/cb9e75aae2940b02e630208bc930f745.webm?t=1758631446\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3151020/extras/cb9e75aae2940b02e630208bc930f745.mp4?t=1758631446\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>The ball control system is completely physics-based.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>If you are looking for an intriguing, rabid and psychological challenge, Easy Ball Game is for you!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Easy Mode</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>learn the path without too obvious dangers, because thanks to some life-saving mats, you won't risk falling all the way down! Plus, you'll unlock an exclusive skin by completing it.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3151020/extras/844f87a37314ea51066b33d97c2a98f5.avif?t=1758631446\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3151020/extras_big/844f87a37314ea51066b33d97c2a98f5.avif?t=1758631446 width=800 height=366 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Impossible Mode</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>In impossible mode there will be no checkpoints and teleports! It was created for those who love the challenge.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3151020/extras/7431f2cdfadd03a8ebc337cda26431d2.avif?t=1758631446\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3151020/extras_big/7431f2cdfadd03a8ebc337cda26431d2.avif?t=1758631446 width=800 height=384 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Quest Mode</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Quest mode offers new paths that will come with new updates and will offer new challenges!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3151020/extras/1dac88657f687fd94f2ebee1c457fa60.avif?t=1758631446\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3151020/extras_big/1dac88657f687fd94f2ebee1c457fa60.avif?t=1758631446 width=800 height=406 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Change Skin</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>In every modes, you can find this funny cylinder which once in, you will be able to change your current skin and unlocked skins!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Teleport Zone (Checkpoints)</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>This little guy here can be found in the normal mode and in the easy mode. This is basically a teleport machine which teleports you on the last checkpoint saved. Checkpoints will be saved every surpassed Zone, so like: ZONE 1- ZONE 2- ZONE 3- ZONE 4.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Hallowen Special - Free DLC</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Venture down the new Hallowen-themed path, filled with frightening dangers, obstacles and waterfalls of blood. Unlock exclusive skins such as the eye and super pumpkin.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3151020/extras/ad016ba8a334223726189587216bfd73.avif?t=1758631446\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3151020/extras_big/ad016ba8a334223726189587216bfd73.avif?t=1758631446 width=800 height=452 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
